title: Into the Wild
description: In this Dateline classic, McKenzie Morgan wants more than anything to learn how to fly. So in August 2013 she takes off on her final solo flight before getting her pilot’s license. All seems well,  until her Cessna 172 vanishes. Keith Morrison reports. Originally aired on NBC on August 24, 2014.
